name: JASMIN IMPÉRATRICE EUGÉNIE
description: Jasmin Impératrice Eugénie was commissioned by a historic French Emperor for his wife, Empress Eugenie, who desired a fragrance of seductive, floral-oriental charm. A sensual fragrance full of warmth and strength, much like the woman for whom it was named. Jasmin Impératrice Eugénie has become a favorite among women who appreciate an opulent scent that takes center stage.
